title: Bobby Lytes interview and more
itunes:title: Bobby Lytes interview and more
description:
Friday 2/9 Today on the show we had Bobby Lytes from Love and Hip Hop Miami and he spoke on being related to Trina, and even spit some bars. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a school in Queens that rejects a student's request to add his name Malcolm X On Senior Sweater. Also, once news broke out that Amber Rose likes to sniff her boo 21 savage underwear we opened up the phone lines to hear what our listeners thought of it.
